{"title":"All new Bontrager AW3 Hard-Case Lite tires get more puncture proof, better traction","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/18/all-new-bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-tires-get-more-flat-resistant-new-rubber-compound/","date":1613664022000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>Many riders go to great lengths to find the lightest and most efficient tire set up on the road. Others, just want to finish their ride without getting a flat. For that second group, there are tires like the Bontrager Hard-Case family. These reinforced tires blend advanced puncture protection with a high-performance road tire – and they’ve just gotten even better.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Bontrager-AW3-Hard-Case-Lite-Reflective-tires-2021-road-bike-durable-5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Bontrager-AW3-Hard-Case-Lite-Reflective-tires-2021-road-bike-durable-5.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" alt=\"Bontrager AW3 Hard-Case lite tire from side\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Bontrager-AW3-Hard-Case-Lite-Reflective-tires-2021-road-bike-durable-5.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Bontrager-AW3-Hard-Case-Lite-Reflective-tires-2021-road-bike-durable-5.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Bontrager-AW3-Hard-Case-Lite-Reflective-tires-2021-road-bike-durable-5-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.co