ead-details-02-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-02-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-02-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-02-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>It’s worth highlighting that the point of these improved designs is to better protect your tubes from getting punctured. These are <em>not</em> tubeless-ready, and Bontrager specifically recommends against trying to set them up tubeless.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03.jpg\" alt=\"Bontrager AW3 Hard-Case close up of tread\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/bontrager-aw3-hard-case-lite-road-tires-tread-details-03-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>All AW3 models feature a slick center tread for high rolling efficiency, but the shoulders feature siping to channel water away from the tread along with recessed dimples for extra cornering traction. The tires also feature their new TR-Endure rubber compound which is said to maintain excellent traction while improving the durability of the tread.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Bontrager-AW3-Hard-Case-Lite-construction-2021.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Bontrager-AW3-Hard-Case-Lite-construction-2021.jpg\" alt=\"Bontrager AW3 Hard-Case Lite tire construction cutaway\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Bontrager-AW3-Hard-Case-Lite-construction-2021.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Bontrager-AW3-Hard-Case-Lite-construction-2021.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Bontrager-AW3-Hard-Case-Lite-construction-2021-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Bontrager-AW3-Hard-Case-Lite-construction-2021-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Bontrager-AW3-Hard-Case-Lite-construction-2021-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Bontrager-AW3-Hard-Case-Lite-construction-2021-768x576.jpg 